ms are demonstrated through two case studies: an illustrative\nlinear system and the autonomous navigation of two spacecraft orbiting an\nasteroid.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 17 Sep 2019 16:33:35 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 7 Jan 2020 00:32:08 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Tue, 14 Apr 2020 18:50:56 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Thu, 13 May 2021 23:22:07 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-05-17"}
