al Feynman graphs. An\n\"oscillating\" nature of these values is discussed. Technical details of the\nrealization are described.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 17 Sep 2019 18:24:08 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 19 Sep 2019 13:28:46 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Wed, 23 Oct 2019 15:46:11 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Mon, 11 Nov 2019 21:38:12 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-11-13"}
