, we present several remarkable experimental results of a\nsupercurrent effect occurring over unusually long distances and clean perfect\nAndreev reflection features.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 17 Sep 2019 23:38:03 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 6 Jul 2020 19:27:33 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-07-08"}
