Data applications can now be expressed declaratively\nin logic-based languages, including Datalog, Prolog, and even SQL, while\nenabling their execution with superior performance and scalability.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 18 Sep 2019 07:08:44 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-09-19"}
