\'a. In the plane, we manage to overcome the use of hypergraph Ramsey\ntheorem and provide polynomial size bounds.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 18 Sep 2019 14:57:24 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 19 Sep 2019 09:08:44 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Mon, 23 Sep 2019 14:37:20 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-09-24"}
